metadata.name: Magu
metadata.description:
I am surprised every time I sell my work.  
Thank you to everyone who has always supported me.  
I'm not a talkative person But this year, I intend to try to talk more with everyone.  Hope I can do it lol. 

This new year everyone will notice that my line art has changed.  I'm not going to abandon my old line art.  but will open another collection instead  I have a bit of a problem with my hands, and this line art helps me relax a lot.  I hope you all like it.
